en.Description: Chateau Westmount Square. Superb Westmount location on the flat. Great building with 24hr security, indoor pool, superb large gym. In house restaurant. Unit is original and vacant for 12years. Needs TLC but great space opportunity. Sold without any legal warranty as to quality.
en.Addenda: Condo fees include: - Garage space fees, gymnasium, 24hr doorman. Exclusive private access to in House Restaurant, valet service for the car, maintenance of the common areas, building insurance.
en.Inclusions: Refrigerator, Stove, Dish-Washer, Washer/Dryer. All horizontals. All inclusions sold as is without any legal warranty, as to quality. An assessment left to be paid of around $5,000 (Depending on the date when accepted).
